OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPatchy rain
OL,6,Fin east clearing this evening with
OL,7,Fsome clear spells for a time tonight.
OL,8,FMore cloud and rain will reach the
OL,9,FIsles and West Highland later in the
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FCloudy with some rain in the
OL,13,Fwest pushing east and weakening, with
OL,14,Fsome brighter spells developing in the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Heavier rain in evening
OL,16,Fwith southerly gales over the Hebrides.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
